<p class="ql-align-center">LEADERSHIP AND INFLUENCING</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>Q: Chevening is looking for individuals whowill be future leaders or influencers in their home countries. Explain how youmeet this requirement, using clear examples of your own leadership andinfluencing skills to support your answer.</strong></p>
<p><strong>4= Outstanding</strong></p>
<p>â€¢ <strong>Held a position of leadership in a professional context </strong>including in avoluntary organization (e.g. a political party, university society, NGO,charity or professional association). </p>
<p>â€¢ Provided strong evidence that they have shaped opinions in their home countrythrough debating, politics, blogs, lecturing and education, social media orpolicy work. The applicant has provided multiple numbers of examples todemonstrate their strong leadership and influencing skills.</p>
<p><strong>3= Very good </strong></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
